:: Copy this file to secrets.bat and fill in your HuggingFace token.
:: secrets.bat is git-ignored — never commit your actual token.
::
:: Get your token at: https://huggingface.co/settings/tokens
:: You also need to accept the user agreements for:
::   - pyannote/speaker-diarization-3.1
::   - pyannote/segmentation-3.0
set "HF_TOKEN=your_huggingface_token_here"
